headline: Analysts start with bullish ratings on Hinge Health on growth potential
summary: Investing.com -- Shares of Hinge Health Inc (NYSE:HNGE) drew bullish coverage from several brokerages as analysts cited the company’s position as a leading provider of virtual physical therapy and highlighted its expanding market opportunity, improving margins, and adoption of artificial intelligence.
